82
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:20,040
The theory of the giant octopus believes that the entire crew, including the captain and his family were taken from the ship

83
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:24,940
One by one, of a huge octopus.

84
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:27,940
